45
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:28,880
So the English word for biscuits has its origins in Latin.

46
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:32,160
It describes cooking bread twice to make it hard.

47
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:36,160
This baking process meant a biscuit could be kept for a long time.

48
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:40,080
